      <title>债券交易员预计美联储 9 月降息将因 CPI 上涨而重现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/traders-fully-price-in-november-fed-rate-cut-after-cool-cpi-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通胀数据低于预期后，交易员对美联储今年降息步伐的预期增强，债券市场预计美联储最早在 9 月份降息的可能性增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/traders-fully-price-in-november-fed-rate-cut-after-cool-cpi-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 12:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度通胀略有缓解，印度储备银行保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/india-s-inflation-eases-slightly-keeping-central-bank-on-guard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度5月份通胀率仅小幅下降，仍高于央行目标，这说明政策制定者需要保持谨慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/india-s-inflation-eases-slightly-keeping-central-bank-on-guard</guid>
